                                    <p>Hosting Services helps you achieve your fiscal goals while maintaining the quality and security demanded by the lending industry.  MortgageFlex offers complete Hosting Services in a certified data center, guaranteeing you high-quality, reliable service.  We are a Microsoft Gold Application Development partner and have been SOC 1 certified since 2006.  We have the experience you need to succeed.</p>
